{
  "id": "RAW_ede6d0",
  "title": "Google Gemini 2.5 解析：推理、多模态与智能体能力的革命性突破，附技术报告英中对照版",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650449519&idx=2&sn=e9532c8cbd2bd876e96894d036722e0d",
  "date": "2025-07-16 13:29:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eac85dd1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJVHummpODmGJbeiaz3gbbJMoMAicnrcUnqymicK691jqa9gZq0ndPUIsWDJRsJYU5XpB6y4DZUN59QA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">前段时间，Google DeepMind发布了Gemini 2.5系列模型技术报告，作为谷歌迄今最强大的AI模型，Gemini 2.5 Pro不仅在传统基准测试中大幅刷新记录，更在</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">长上下文理解</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">复杂推理</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">和</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">多模态智能体</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能力上实现质的飞跃。本文将深度解析这一技术里程碑的核心突破与潜在影响。</span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box;height: 0px;overflow: visible;margin: 1rem auto;border-right: none;border-bottom: 2px solid;border-left: none;border-image: initial;border-top: none;opacity: 1;width: 100px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 1.4rem;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.3;font-size: 28px;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;letter-spacing: -0.05em;color: rgb(33, 33, 33);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一、架构革新：从混合专家到思维引擎</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 2.5系列基于</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">稀疏混合专家模型（MoE）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;架构，但进行了关键升级：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">动态路由优化</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过改进token到专家的分配策略，计算效率提升40%（相比Gemini 1.5 Pro）</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">训练稳定性突破</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">采用</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">分阶段静默数据损坏检测</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">技术，将故障定位时间从小时级缩短至分钟级</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">TPUv5p超算级训练</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跨数据中心8960芯片集群同步训练，93.4%时间用于有效计算</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“Thinking”机制创新</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;font-size: 14px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 32px;overflow: auto;display: block;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);background: rgb(246, 246, 246);max-width: 100%;padding: 16px;white-space: pre-wrap;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"># Thinking机制伪代码示例</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">def generate_response(query): &nbsp; &nbsp; thought_tokens = allocate_thinking_budget(query) &nbsp;</span></span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"># 动态分配计算资源</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;for _ in range(thought_tokens): &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; internal_state = refine_thought(internal_state, query) &nbsp;</span></span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"># 迭代推理</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;return finalize_response(internal_state)</span></span></pre>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">该机制允许模型在响应前进行</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">数万次前向传播</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，显著提升复杂问题解决能力。在AIME 2025数学竞赛基准上，思考预算增加使准确率从72%跃升至88%。</span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box;height: 0px;overflow: visible;margin: 1rem auto;border-right: none;border-bottom: 2px solid;border-left: none;border-image: initial;border-top: none;opacity: 1;width: 100px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 1.4rem;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.3;font-size: 28px;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;letter-spacing: -0.05em;color: rgb(33, 33, 33);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">二、多模态理解：突破时空限制</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 2.5 Pro实现了前所未有的多模态处理能力：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3小时视频解析</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过视觉token压缩技术（每帧66 token vs 旧版258 token）</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跨模态转换</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可将讲座视频实时转化为交互式测验应用（Baddepudi et al., 2025）</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">音频流式处理</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">支持24种语言的对话式语音交互，情感识别误差降低35%</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在VideoMME视频理解基准上，Gemini 2.5 Pro以</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">84.3%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;准确率超越GPT 4.1的72%，尤其在时空推理任务（如寻找跨镜头关联事件）上优势显著。</span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box;height: 0px;overflow: visible;margin: 1rem auto;border-right: none;border-bottom: 2px solid;border-left: none;border-image: initial;border-top: none;opacity: 1;width: 100px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 1.4rem;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.3;font-size: 28px;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;letter-spacing: -0.05em;color: rgb(33, 33, 33);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">三、智能体生态：从编码到自主决策</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告展示了Gemini作为智能体平台的核心能力：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">代码革命</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LiveCodeBench得分从30.5%(1.5 Pro)飙升至</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">74.2%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，SWE-bench验证任务提升33%</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini Deep Research</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网络研究代理在Humanity's Last Exam基准半年内从7.95%提升至</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">32.4%</span></span></strong></p></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Pokémon通关案例</span></span></strong>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在813小时游戏过程中展现</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">长程规划能力</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，解决包含150步操作的迷宫难题</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <figure style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em;box-sizing: border-box;display: block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n  </figure>\n  <hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box;height: 0px;overflow: visible;margin: 1rem auto;border-right: none;border-bottom: 2px solid;border-left: none;border-image: initial;border-top: none;opacity: 1;width: 100px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Work Sans&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 0px 1.4rem;font-weight: 700;line-height: 1.3;font-size: 28px;font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;letter-spacing: -0.05em;color: rgb(33, 33, 33);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span 